---
title: Beef Tenderloin with Demi-Glace Sauce with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Lemony Brussels Sprouts
description: You haven’t tasted steak quite like this before: this melt-in-your-mouth beef tenderloin is spooned with a rich, rosemary-flecked pan sauce to bring its meatiness to the maximum. On the side, creamy garlic mashed potatoes and crispy roasted lemon Brussels sprouts so good, you may not want to share.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-tenderloin-topped-demi-glace-cddc6974.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/beef-tenderloin-topped-demi-glace-5d9e13a7168569635b1a884b-15c1d76a.pdf
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 32 g
